OL,4,Csmuggling ring from Welsh car wash
OL,6,FTwo men who allegedly ran a
OL,7,Ftrafficking ring from a car wash in
OL,8,FWales sent messages about the "people
OL,9,Fsmuggling business," a court has heard.
OL,11,FDilshad Shamo, 41, and Ali Khdir, 40,
OL,12,Fboth from Caerphilly, are accused of
OL,13,Funlawfully moving hundreds of people
OL,14,Fthrough Europe, by arranging the
OL,15,Fmovement of migrants in boats, HGVs
OL,16,Fand cars from Iraq, Iran and Syria.
