OL,3,CTwo men accused of running people-
OL,4,Csmuggling ring from Welsh car wash
OL,6,FKhdir, who was born in Iran, and
OL,7,FShamo, originally from Iraq, owned and
OL,8,Foperated the Fast Track Hand Car Wash
OL,9,Fin Caerphilly, where people
OL,10,Ftrafficking is alleged to have been
OL,11,Forganised.
OL,13,FCardiff Crown Court was shown various
OL,14,Fmessages allegedly from the defendants
OL,15,Fon Tuesday, 12 November, including
OL,16,Fsome referring to the "people
OL,17,Fsmuggling business".
