OL,6,FBoth Khdir and Shamo deny five counts
OL,7,Fof conspiring to breach migration laws
OL,8,Fin Italy, Romania, Croatia and Germany
OL,9,Fto bring people into EU countries.
OL,11,FAll the offences are alleged to have
OL,12,Ftaken place between September 2022 and
OL,13,FApril 2023.
OL,15,FVoice and written messages appear to
OL,16,Fshow Khdir and Shamo speaking with
OL,17,Fvarious people across Europe, Turkey
OL,18,Fand Iraq, discussing routes, passports
OL,19,Fand money changing hands.
