OL,6,FThe jury was also shown video clips,
OL,7,Fincluding of people on various routes,
OL,8,Fas well as audio recordings taken by
OL,9,Fthe police using listening devices
OL,10,Fhidden in the defendant's vehicles.
OL,12,FOne message showed a man named
OL,13,F"Chomani" saying to Khdir: "Hi Uncle
OL,14,Fhave you got any people in Istanbul?"
OL,16,FA voice recording of Khdir's response
OL,17,Fwas played to the jury, where he said
OL,18,Fhe had been busy working at "my car
OL,19,Fwash" and there were people who wanted
OL,20,FTurkish visas, adding: "You are aware
OL,21,Fhow people smuggling business is".
