OL,6,FShamo told him there were Croatian,
OL,7,FSlovenian and Italian cars ready,
OL,8,Fadding: "Just hand them to me and I'll
OL,9,Fget them over the border" and "just
OL,10,Fsay that Dilshad has got cars on both
OL,11,Fsides".
OL,13,FIn another translated recording, Shamo
OL,14,Fsaid: "All agents are under my
OL,15,Fcontrol, including those in Bosnia,
OL,16,FSerbia, Turkey, Italy and Slovenia.
OL,18,F"We have cars and if they cross the
OL,19,Fborder to Turkey, I will manage the
OL,20,Frest. I cannot take them straight away
OL,21,Fto British migration."
