OL,6,FMs Gaunt told the jury the accused
OL,7,Fwere also secretly recorded while they
OL,8,Fwere being taken to the police station
OL,9,Ffollowing their arrests on April 13,
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FShe said: "The defendants were
OL,13,Fconveyed to the police station in NCA
OL,14,F(National Crime Agency) vehicles.
OL,16,F"There was a conversation between
OL,17,FShamo and Khdir in Kurdish, whilst
OL,18,Fnext to each other in the police cars
OL,19,Fwhich was covertly recorded by the
OL,20,Fpolice, and was later translated.
