OL,6,F"During this conversation, Shamo told
OL,7,FKhdir, 'just tell them that we didn't
OL,8,Ffacilitate anyone to enter the country
OL,9,Fillegally. They'll only ask us some
OL,10,Fquestions; it's not related to
OL,11,Fanything else'."
OL,13,FShe said they told each other their
OL,14,Fphones had been confiscated by the
OL,15,Fpolice, with Khdir having given them
OL,16,Fhis passcode, while Shamo said he had
OL,17,Fgiven an incorrect number.
